name: Air Transat A310-304 [C-GTSW] Takeoff from Edmonton Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
Follow me on Flickr: https://www.flickr.com/photos/dude8472productions/

Here we have one of the many "sun flights" that operate from Edmonton International Airport, Air Transat #518 to Cancun, Mexico, taxiing and making a beautiful overhead takeoff off of YEG's runway 12. I recently spent another day of spotting in Edmonton, so expect a couple more videos in the new year! Enjoy.

Thanks for watching! Please comment, rate, and subscribe!
